title: Kang Han Na Is Ready To Win At Any Cost To Yoo Jae Suk’s Surprise On “Running Man”
text:
Pin Display.Sharethrough.Soompi.1x1 
On the March 26 episode of SBS’s “ Running Man ,” Jun So Min , Lee Se Young , Kang Han Na, Park Jin Joo , GFRIEND’s Umji, and Choi Tae Joon appeared as part of the “Princess Special.” 
During the show, Kang Han Na participated in a history quiz couple race along with the other members and guests, but was caught on camera multiple times secretly looking over at Yoo Jae Suk ’s notes for the answers. Soompi.Display.News.English.300x250.BTF Soompi.Mobile.English.300x250.ATF 
Yoo Jae Suk, who started noticing what she was doing, said once everyone was outside, “If I’m going to be honest, Kang Han Na has a very cunning side.” 
Seems like the actress is very competitive!
